node.text:
Here are some of my fav/go-to sets!!! Comment down below if you have any questions so I can answer those for you!!
-
I am an XS in EVERYTHING! For reference: 5ft tall | 105lbs | Waist: 23in
-
I will have a link in my bio + I will post swipe up links before the sale! If you choose to shop through my link it does support me directly 💛💖

Hitting ya with a LEGS & GLUTES workout 👏🏼 Some staple exercises for a killer leg day! Give this one a GO 👊🏼

1️⃣ 3 sets / 12 heels elevated goblet squats

2️⃣ 3 sets / 8 RDLs

3️⃣ 4 sets / 15, 12, 10, 8 hip thrusts
Increase the weight each set as you go down in reps

4️⃣ 3 sets / 8 (each) deficit lunges

5️⃣ 3 sets / 15 frog pumps

Wearing @gymshark apex shorts + v neck training sports bra // Song: Head & Heart by Joel Corry, MNEK
-
#legday #legworkout #legdayworkout #workoutmotivation #fitness #fit #gym #gymmotivation #legsworkout #motivation #fitnessmotivation #workoutideas #workoutvideo

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Alex Rice | Workouts on August 02, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and standing.

node.text:
M O N D A Y 🌟 also the start of a new month! Whaaaat, how is it August?!! Kicking off the week with a leg day later 🤘🏼 At the moment, my workout split has been 2 upper body workouts and 2 lower body workouts! I have no set cardio routine, but of course daily walkies 🐶🐶 and I’ve mentioned I’ve added in some runs here and there!

If I miss a workout or workouts get moved around.. it’s ok with me! Following a workout split helps give me more structure. But it’s all about finding what works best for you, and sometimes for me that might mean skipping a workout!

Wearing @gymshark hyper amplify shorts + v neck training sports bra (not released yet!)
-
#workoutmotivation #mondaymotivation #legday #legworkout #mondayworkout #gymshark #liftweights #motivation #fitness #fit #workout #fitnessmotivation #gym #gymworkout #homeworkout #gymtime

Time for some BOULDER SHOULDER work 👏🏼 there’s nothing like a shoulder burner 🥲 LET’S GOOOO

1️⃣ 3 sets / 8 (each) single arm lateral raise

2️⃣ 4 sets / 10 Arnold press

3️⃣ 3 sets / 12 rear delt pull

4️⃣ 3 sets / 10 incline front raise

5️⃣ 3 sets / 10 alternating lateral raises

Wearing new @gymshark Mercury collection releasing today at 11am PST 🌟 link in bio!
-
#workoutmotivation #bouldershoulders #upperbodyworkout #dumbbellonly #fit #fitnessmotivation #workoutideas #gym #motivation #shoulderworkout #fitness

node.text:
LEGS & GLUTES!! I was toast after this one 🥵 Let’s get after it!!

1️⃣ 3 sets / 10 (each) lateral lunges
2️⃣ 4 sets / 10 barbell hip thrust
3️⃣ 3 sets / 12 goblet squat
4️⃣ 3 sets / 8 reverse lunges
5️⃣ 3 sets / 12 hamstring bridge - like a glute bridge but scoot away from the bench and focus on your hamstrings doing the work

Wearing @gymshark vital seamless 2.0 shorts + v neck training sports bra (not released yet!)
-
#workoutmotivation #fitnessreel #fitness #legday #legworkout #legdayworkout #workoutvideo #reels #workoutideas #fit #liftweights #gymworkout #gymmotivation

node.text:
Happy Tuesday!! Whatcha training today?? I have a shoulder day planned and also a run… 😳 running does notttt come easy to me, but that accomplishment you feel after completing something that you felt was really challenging is 🙌🏼🙌🏼🙌🏼 That’s my favorite part about working out in general.. the challenge of certain exercises or workouts and those post workout endorphins 👏🏼

Wearing @gymshark Apex leggings + training bandeau
-
#workout #workoutmotivation #fitness #fit #motivation #liftweights #workingout #gymshark #gymmotivation #gym #healthandfitness #health #fitmotivation

Starting the week off strong and sweatyyy with a LEGS & GLUTES workout 👏🏼 let’s get after it this week!!

1️⃣ 3 sets / 8 DB sumo squats w/ pulse

2️⃣ 3 sets / 6-8 heavy Bulgarian split squats

3️⃣ 4 sets / 10 front squats

4️⃣ 3 sets / 10 sumo RDLs

5️⃣ 3 sets / 12 single leg DB hip thrust

Wearing @gymshark legacy fitness shorts + NEW (not released yet) scoop neck sports bra // Song: In Your Eyes by Robin Schulz ft. Alida
-
#mondaymotivation #workoutmotivation #legday #legworkout #legs #legdayworkout #mondaylegday #workout #fitness #fit #gym #fitnessmotivation #gymmotivation

node.text:
AB WORKOUT time! Let’s gooooo 👏🏼 

2-3 rounds - give yourself a rest after each round!

TAG your ab workout partner 🌟

1️⃣ 8 reps / (each) boat hold with press
2️⃣ 12 reps / weighted leg extension variation
3️⃣ 10 reps / hip raises
4️⃣ 12 reps / (each) alternating leg extensions

Wearing @gymshark new training leggings + new v neck training so does bra (not released yet!)
-
#fitnessreel #fitness #fitmotivation #reels #workoutmotivation #motivation #reelsworkout #homeworkout #dumbbell #absworkout #abs #quickworkout #reelsfitness #fit #gym #circuit

node.text:
let’s hit some upper body 🔥 it’s a PUSH workout! Some boulder shoulder and a little chest and tri’s 👏🏼 let’s get after it!!

1️⃣ 3 sets / 10 alternating front raise

2️⃣ 4 sets / 10 tempo seated shoulder press
Slowww on the way down - 3 sec

3️⃣ 3 sets / 12 single arm tricep extension

4️⃣ 3 sets / 8 DB bench press

5️⃣ 3 sets / 8-10 bench plyo push ups

Wearing @gymshark new Mercury set, coming soooon 👀 Song: Paradise by Bazzi
-
#workoutmotivation #bouldershoulders #fit #gymworkout #homeworkout #dumbbellonly #upperbodyworkout #upperbody #fitness #motivation #fitnessmotivation #liftweights

node.text:
Hitting you with a sweaty LEGS & GLUTES session 👊🏼 I was toast after this one.. Lets gooooo!

1️⃣ 3 sets / 8 1 3/4 goblet squat
2️⃣ 4 sets / 10 Sumo deadlifts
3️⃣ 3 sets / 6-8 (each) deficit lunges
4️⃣ 3 sets / 12 dumbbell RDLs
5️⃣ 3 sets / 12 heels elevated hamstring bridge - focusing on the hammies with this one, scoot away from the bench!

Wearing @gymshark NEW mercury set, coming sooooon 👀 // Song: Rain On Me by Lady Gaga, Ariana Grande
-
#workoutmotivation #legday #legworkout #legs #legdayworkout #motivation #fitness #fit #liftweights #fitmotivation #workout #homeworkout #gymworkout #gymmotivation

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Alex Rice | Workouts on July 19, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, standing and activewear.

node.text:
H a p p y 🌼 M o n d a y! Starting the week off strong stronggg with a leg day, anyone else!?? Last week my workouts were all over the place. The motivation just wasn’t there, and thats ok!!That’s just how it goes some weeks! Buuut it’s Monday, it’s a new week🤘🏼let’s get after it!!

Wearing @gymshark Apex shorts + new v neck training sports bra (not released yet!)
-
#workoutmotivation #mondayworkout #fittips #mondaymotivation #motivation #fitness #fit #workout #monday #gym #gymmotivation #liftweights #legday #legworkout #gymideas

Back at it with some UPPER BODY 🔥 hitting a little bit of everything with this one! Shoulders, arms, back, and chest 👏🏼👏🏼

1️⃣ 3 sets / 8 heavy alternating bicep curls
2️⃣ 3 sets / 12 (each) kneeling Arnold press
3️⃣ 3 sets / 12 underhand rows
4️⃣ 3 sets / 10 close grip DB bench press
5️⃣ 3 sets / 12 tricep kickbacks

Wearing @gymshark NEW training leggings + v neck training sports bra // Song: Go Somewhere by KREAM, Rani
-
#workoutvideo #upperbodyworkout #fitness #workoutmotivation #motivation #workout #gym #bouldershoulders #workoutideas #gymworkout #homeworkout #fit #liftweights
